
---

##  Error Types Captured

| Type | Description |
|----|----|
| JS_ERROR | Runtime JavaScript exceptions |
| PROMISE_REJECTION | Unhandled async failures |
| NETWORK_ERROR | Failed HTTP requests |

---

## Dashboard Capabilities

- View all captured errors
- Filter by error type
- Search error messages
- View timestamps & browser info
- Export logs for debugging

---

##  Demo Mode

The app includes buttons to:
- Trigger JS errors
- Trigger Promise rejections
- Trigger Network failures

Perfect for live demos and testing.

---

## Tech Stack

- React (Vite)
- Tailwind CSS
- Chart.js
- LocalStorage (IndexedDB-ready)
- Modern ES6+

---

##  Roadmap

- IndexedDB support
- Remote server sync
- Authentication
- Alert notifications
- Error deduplication
- Session tracking

---

## Installation

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
